    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"ariadne-entry\"><p><strong>Source:</strong> Ariadne's Book of Legends - Alpha v1.2, p. 50-53.</p><p>Wellspring of Ki</p><p>Starting at 21st level, you learn to enter a state of profound wholeness that rejuvenates and invigorates your soul. You can enter this state as an action. For the next minute, you regain 3 Focus points at the start of each of your turns. Once you enter this state, you cannot do so again until you finish a long rest.</p></div>",
